[b][color=#6aa84f][size=5][u]■About this mod
[/u][/size][/color][/b]
 　・This mod adds  Elven "healer" followers:  "Sela" and "Noemie","Noela". (Available together or separately.) 
 　・They are standalone followers and do not require additional mods.　
    ・They are set as Essential.　
    ・Their body can be selected during the installation.
     →Noemie ＆ Noela （UNPB・CBBE・SeveNBase）×（Weight　0 ・50 ・100）
　  →Sela（UNPB・CBBE・SeveNBase・[b][color=#ff00ff]7BCH[/color][/b]）×（Weight　0 ・50 ・100）

        [color=#ff00ff]7BCH is the body type of 7B-based, It is even more big boobs!
[/color]        [color=#ff00ff]It is very wonderful MOD！
[/color]　　 [url=http://mitakusaner.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-581.html#comment2131]→The author of the site[/url]
    
    ・They use the recovery magic in combat.


[img]http://i.imgur.com/y0xtNsP.png[/img]

      【Sela】  
        ・She has blue hair styled in a bob cut. Alternative medium-length hair style under optional files.     
        ・Combat style : Various ice magic and recovery magic.
        ・Location        : Sleeping Giant Inn (Riverwood).   
        ・Japanesue Voice actor　: 霞月葵　様
[color=#f4f4f4]        ・Her custom voice version now supports marriage function!　　
　　　→When you talked to her equipped with "Amulet of Mara", marriage event occurs.[/color]

     【Noemie】     
       ・A blonde, medium length haired girl, younger of the two. Alternative bunched hair style (twin-tail in Japanese) under optional files.    
       ・Combat style :　Use of Archery and recovery magic.
       ・Location　　 　 :  Temple of Kynareth (Whiterun).     
　 　・Japanesue Voice actor　: Otoha　様
        ・Her custom voice version now supports marriage function!　　
　　　→When you talked to her equipped with "Amulet of Mara", marriage event occurs.

     【Noela】
　　 ・She is the twin sister of Noemi .    
       ・A brunet, medium length haired girl, younger of the two. Alternative bunched hair style (twin-tail in Japanese) under optional files.     
       ・Combat style :　Use of  scythe and recovery magic.
       ・Location　　 　 :  Dragonsreach (Whiterun).     
　 　・Japanesue Voice actor　: 瀬ノ内 ゆあ　様

[/size][b]【Sela and Noemie】[/b]
[color=#f4f4f4]It is possible to talk to girls, you can be free to change the two types of recovery magic（Grand Healing/Heal other）.[/color]

[/color]
In conversation during non-combat, they will treat health and disease.

she will use the "Heal other".

They will be able to recover the followers.
→When girls are followers state, please talk to another followers.
    Dialog box is displayed to its followers to the recipient's recovery magic.
    In this dialog, you can in the recipient's recovery magic up to four people.
    They will use the recovery magic When the health of the recipient is less than 60％t．[color=#fff2cc]

セラ・ノエミ・ノエラは、フォロワーを回復することができます。
→彼女達がフォロワー状態の時に、他のフォロワーに話しかけてください。
　専用のダイアログで、そのフォロワーを回復魔法を受ける対象者に選択できます。
　回復魔法の対象者は4人まで指定できます。
　セラ・ノエミ・ノエラは、指定した対象者のヘルスが60％以下になった時に回復魔法を使用します。
